::Magmatron::

    He sat in his command chair watching, through cameras, as Phobia left. He 
never really trusted that spider, but he thought it might be good for 
relations if he was nice to people who would be ememies someday. Like 
Pantron, he knew he proboly wouldn't come back, and he really didn't care. He 
also knew that Bobertron proboly would side with Pantron, but he couldn't be 
sure on that one. 
    He set the Autoguns to reconize Phobias' and Pantron's signal as an 
ememy, so they would have a big surprise if they came back.
